headline: Is It Too Late To Consider DoorDash After Its 341% Three Year Surge?
summary: If you are wondering whether DoorDash is still worth buying after its big run, or if the easy money has already been made, you are not alone. This is exactly what we are going to unpack here. With the stock at $226.98 after climbing 0.7% over the last week, 9.7% over the last month, 33.0% year to date, and 26.5% over the past year on top of a 341.3% gain over 3 years, investors are clearly pricing in a lot of growth and a shifting risk profile. headline: DataLane Secures $27M to Deliver Identity Graph of 20M Local Businesses
summary: NEW YORK, December 16, 2025--DataLane, the identity graph for local businesses, today announced a $22.5 million Series A led by Amplify Partners with participation from Harry Stebbings, founder of 20VC, Basis Set, Mischief, and others. DataLane is building the first highly accurate identity platform for every local business in America — a LinkedIn for the offline economy — so companies like DoorDash, Square, Paychex, and Motorola can find, verify, and reach real business owners with unmatched pr
